    "question_id" : 79694518,
    "body" : "<p>I don't think you do it wrongly.</p>\n<p>Let me tell you what I did to work:</p>\n<p><strong>1. app.conf</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"lang-json prettyprint-override\"><code>z {\n  useSecret: ${SECRET}\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>2. local.conf</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"lang-json prettyprint-override\"><code>\nSECRET: &quot;fooBar&quot;\ninclude &quot;app.conf&quot;\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>3. Java method</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"lang-java prettyprint-override\"><code>\nConfig conf = ConfigFactory.parseFile(new File(&quot;./src/main/resources/local.conf&quot;))\n        .resolve();\nSystem.out.println(conf.getString(&quot;z.useSecret&quot;));\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>Output:</strong></p>\n<pre><code>fooBar\n</code></pre>\n<p>I think the <code>resolve()</code> at the end would make it work for you!</p>\n",
